The paper deals with image registration using deep learning techniques, specifically a spatial transformer network and a convolutional autoencoder. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of deep learning also suggests that the paper may fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with electron microscopy images, which may also fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
